description: Merged open source topographic and bathymetric data from multiple sources. Topographic data includes: ALOS DSM, AHN Netherlands, Greenland DEM, USGS NED, Canadian DEM, Australian DEM, and REMA Mosaic. Bathymetric data from: GEBCO and EMODnet. See [the Wiki](https://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/BED/References) for further information about this dataset.
title: Elevation
license_use: Elevation Data Products (Elevation). - The purpose of the Elevation Data Product is to support the analysis and interpretation of the other Data Products by the User. The Elevation Data Product should NOT be used for navigation or for any other purpose involving safety at sea or on land.
